[Why & How]
Enable root clock optimization options for dcn35
for power savings

Reviewed-by: Nicholas Kazlauskas <nicholas.kazlauskas@amd.com>
Acked-by: Hersen Wu <hersenxs.wu@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Daniel Miess <daniel.miess@amd.com>
